videos.description: Ana Owens feeds Shanice Johnson, who slips behind defenders for a layup.
videos.headline: Cincinnati's Johnson goes backdoor for layup

videos.description: Gabby Williams hits a fast-break layup off of a steal by Kia Nurse.
videos.headline: UConn's pressure creates transition layup

videos.description: Napheesa Collier chases down the loose ball and Katie Lou Samuelson rewards her with a pass for a corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: UConn's Samuelson rewards Collier for hustle

videos.description: Kyla Irwin steals the ball and Katie Lou Samuelson throws a long outlet pass to Kia Nurse for an and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: UConn's tenacious D sets up Nurse layup
